{"tid":442603,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"天空之城 純音樂廣東話填詞","createTime":"2017-10-20T19:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T09:23:34.000Z","uid":153665,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6dbb940141353d87e4848f2e1bde002977bb9f1b","tid":442603,"uid":153665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:37:52.000Z","msg":"天空之城 純音樂廣東話填詞<br />\n<br />\n查實我入到lift後<br />\n就感覺有啲臭<br />\n味覺係好荒謬<br />\n煨蕃薯 同荷蘭豆<br />\n<br />\n嘗試學會忍受<br />\n但我的確好想嘔<br />\n若撐下去 氧氣快已不夠<br />\n點先去到三十樓<br />\n<br />\n在這升降機跟你<br />\n聞屁味至想死<br />\n唔係你 仲有邊位咁離奇<br />\n想講丟你老味<br />\n<br />\n是可怕的一督屁<br />\n困室裡冇得避<br />\n沒一口新鮮空氣<br />\n我想切咗個鼻<br />\n<br />\n詞：Chef L&eacute; mon<br />\n曲：久石讓<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DVrfn0UAKbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDVrfn0UAKbQ&d=SqI5g1WaY6r%2Fyy9H4DuS9DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c8910e5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DVrfn0UAKbQ</a>"},{"pid":"3862d70d5e4b47fc509ee7c29a5230d3b6a3b02d","tid":442603,"uid":18877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T20:25:12.000Z","msg":"唔好意思個屁臭親你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31486d4d9e3ff9700acc261be907830251cdd063","tid":442603,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線嫁啲歌詞<br />\n快啲搵因莉唱"},{"pid":"5736d8ec690a028d7168605874b2c68757c550b2","tid":442603,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87652d18baa70d0b6ce8d8d81213322f083e1dd2","tid":442603,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"